title: Girls Soccer Roundup: Wildcats win on the road
text:
Girls Soccer Roundup: Wildcats win on the road 10:52 p.m. EDT October 12, 2015 File photo CONNECT TWEET LINKEDIN COMMENT EMAIL MORE 
Woodmore 2, Van Buren 1 
The Wildcats (13-1-1, 9-0) earned a road win over Van Buren on Monday. The score at the half was 1-0, Woodmore.
